      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults patients, &gt;/=18 years of age

          -  Chronic Hepatitis C, Genotype 1 and 4

          -  HCV RNA &gt;/=50,000 IU/mL

          -  treatment-naive

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with cirrhosis or incomplete/transition to cirrhosis

          -  Patients with other forms of liver disease, HIV infection, hepatocellular carcinoma or
             severe cardiac disease
      </textblock>
